        // Using the formula $a_n - a_{n-1}$: $a_3 - a_2 = 4 - 3 = 1$. This matches.
        // The example partition: Class 1: [6, 4, 2] (median 4). Class 2: [5, 1, 3] (median 3). Diff = 1.
