        // 3. All chosen numbers 2*k are within the range [1, 4n].
        //    The smallest chosen number is 2*n.
        //    The largest chosen number is 2*(2n-1) = 4n-2.
        //    Both 2n and 4n-2 are within [1, 4n].

        for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
